---
title: Quick Italian Pesto Beef Toss with Ciabatta Croutons
description: Part panzanella, part steak dinner, all delicious. This quick beef and rocket crouton toss with pesto and pine nuts will keep you satisfied while tasting fresh and delicious. Nice one!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b72260730006c3e0b1364b2-b978aeae.jpg
